{
  "id": "RAW_1fea2732",
  "title": "第一批通过 VibeCoding 赚钱的人出现了：省 140 万、售卖会员、营收近万，他们都不是技术背景",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&mid=2247487511&idx=1&sn=4e7797b303d51285b3e7ef4a74ad5095",
  "date": "2025-12-18 23:08:00",
  "author": "花叔",
  "siteName": "花叔",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #fff !important;padding: 40px 12px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年2月，OpenAI联合创始人Andrej Karpathy提出了Vibe Coding的概念：用自然语言描述想法，AI生成代码，开发者不需要真的懂编程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100003849\" data-ratio=\"0.7824074074074074\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1a61a4d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70P6VwGIUAo9L9IubwMibFWxgtrb4bru3GWD7fyVn1Diam41KzGjgaZlHJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个概念的提出算是开启了Vibe Coding的元年，从去年下半年开始，AI的Coding能力大幅提升，让开发门槛大幅降低。YC W25批次的数据显示，25%的创业公司代码库95%由AI生成。国内外许多大厂也开始重视自己研发线的代码中有多少是由AI生成的这一指标。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vibe Coding确实让开发变简单了，理论上人人都能做应用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但作为一个持续不断使用AI去开发产品的AI Native Coder，一个持续普及AI编程的博主，我发现一个现象。就是我还在持续做Cursor、Claude Code等AI编程工具的教学，为什么会需要做这些教学呢？因为这些工具确实对普通人有一些门槛，AI确实帮用户简化了很多困难，0基础的普通人做出产品确实是有可能的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但对大多数人来说，代码生成出来了，该如何部署上线让其他人也能用呢？如何接入地图能力、AI功能？如何实现注册登录、支付系统？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些问题，对互联网产研背景的人来说不难。但对第一次尝试做应用的人来说，这是真正的门槛。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以最近一年，出现了一批\"更集成化\"的VibeCoding平台。比如Google最近很出圈的可以直接生成应用的AIStudio，比如lovable、Bolt.new等等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而国内在这个方向上探索最多，做得最好的，则可能是「秒哒」。他们不只是生成代码，还提供了从部署、集成到商业化的完整解决方案。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这才是真正适合普通人上手即用的VibeCoding工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003856\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e54a0d42&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PhUw39icXdgUicvglWXKZMB9NxTwwpjGiasPicDhllicaB7kibQTMWTcLGic3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实我知道秒哒有几个月的时间了，但真正让我惊讶的，是最近看到的一些用户案例:</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">油气职工用秒哒做了生产优化系统，节省成本140万；琴行老板做了AI小说工具，通过售卖会员实现商业化；口腔教师做了儿童健康小程序，测试阶段营收近万元。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些人，都不是技术背景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一批用秒哒赚钱的人，已经出现了。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我对秒哒的一些印象</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">说起来，我和秒哒倒是有些特别的渊源。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一次是在今年的百度云智大会。当时我作为开发者，和秒哒产品负责人朱广翔在国家会议中心一起参加圆桌对话。主题是\"小团队怎么用AI Coding做出好产品\"。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003850\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6657407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=577fd88f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PPdYpv37pBka1Oc8uJFFY8F5LPDBOW5DOCOIA7tKsQnXqgCndcACE5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">对话开始前，我现场试了试秒哒。10分钟，我用自然语言描述，让秒哒生成了小猫补光灯的网页版。对话、生成、调整、部署，整个过程非常丝滑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003853\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5657407407407408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=72e23eac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PXpdeSprMYTzksgsYhXtFwic0nBXbWHGo7XKBB4sRYfpRLwCM2glhI4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二次是在一个小学生工作坊。我去给20多个小学生分享Vibe Coding。当时还很犹豫，如果要让小学生在短短1个多小时的分享里，咋能又get我的理念，又能真正实操上手去体验究竟什么是vibe coding的感觉呢？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003852\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0acf5f71&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PmB96rmn6HJppVe99uIkalobCANa7JMLj2qvjiaUbUWf5Als8QYXNMRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">犹豫半天发现只有秒哒是让他们没有语言和访问障碍，又能轻松上手的最合适的选择。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果让我惊喜。半小时内，很多小学生就成功做出了应用:作业助手、智能计算器、数学知识扫描仪、AI网名生成器……等等</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003857\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a220182&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PwzAS78mqWelbAxJtO9IQw67bJvstqNZuEBqWeQuVWvia6dJciaRMua2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">连小学生都能半小时做出应用，这说明秒哒的易用性确实到位了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但更重要的是，这些应用不是简单的HTML页面，是真的有前后端、有交互的应用。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么秒哒\"更适合中国宝宝\"？</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">VibeCoding工具很多，为什么说秒哒\"更适合中国宝宝\"？</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #d32f2f !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;margin: 35px 0 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 微信生态，天然流量入口</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国最大的社交平台是微信，不是Instagram或Facebook。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒支持一键生成微信小程序，直接发布到微信生态。对中国开发者来说，这意味着天然的流量入口。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之前用过bolt.new，体验确实不错，但它做的是Web应用。在中国，想让用户用你的Web应用？先得让他们记住你的域名。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但小程序不一样。用户在微信里搜索、扫码、转发，天然的流量分发机制。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是本土化的优势。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #d32f2f !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;margin: 35px 0 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 百度生态加持，插件丰富</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒内置了百度的独家插件:</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">百度AI搜索:中文搜索理解能力最强</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">百度地图:本土化最好的地图服务</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">百度AI工具:图文生成、语音合成、文字识别等</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户要调用任何能力，只需@即可，大大降低接入成本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我以前也吐槽过传统无代码平台:\"有一套程序逻辑逼迫你去学习理解和适应，尤其当这个平台的交互逻辑主要由纯工程师思维的人设计，文档又写得很烂的时候，那用起来将是一个巨大的灾难。\"</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但VibeCoding不一样。你不需要学习平台的逻辑，你只需要说你想要什么。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒把这个做到了极致。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #d32f2f !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;margin: 35px 0 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 商业化闭环，不只是玩具</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之前评价bolt.new:\"更适合新手入门，有种无代码建站的惊艳感，但是你想细究，想融入登录、注册、支付，没那么好用。\"</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003851\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3055555555555556\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4d84876&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PrZRfAnibFh5WRqoxRgCWVccDLvr6DPMVAyCBwX3Az5Es6nffYqjjrsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多VibeCoding工具都是这样:做原型很快，但做商业产品很难。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒不一样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它内置了短信验证码、用户登录、微信支付等功能。从开发到流量到收益，全链路打通。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是为什么会有人用秒哒赚钱。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一批用秒哒赚钱的人，已经出现了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">截至目前，秒哒平台已生成超过50万个商业应用，服务千万级用户，创造价值超50亿元。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，第一批用秒哒赚钱的人，已经出现了。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #d32f2f !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;margin: 35px 0 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\"><span leaf=\"\">案例1:油气职工省了140万</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a 