=\"\">他的初衷很简单:\"想让写小说盈利的人可以用AI写小说。\"</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有技术背景，但有想法+有需求，秒哒让他把想法变成了能赚钱的产品。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003855\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6490872210953347\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"986\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87062c42&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PAJ99E7lMmPuIe7zZ1MvIXTo9s7gAAhAfryclEbn9kyX8tb04qXWYRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">案例链接：<a href=\"http://xiaoshuo.yymaiya.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">http://xiaoshuo.yymaiya.cn/</a></span></span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #d32f2f !important;line-height: 1.5 !important;margin: 35px 0 20px;padding-left: 16px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;\"><span leaf=\"\">案例3:口腔教师的护牙小程序</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者是口腔预防教育从业者，做了\"蜗牛牙牙\"儿童口腔健康小程序。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对孩子刷牙习惯不佳、家长缺乏专业护牙指导等问题，她打造了集趣味体验与专业指导于一体的服务体系。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供训练营服务，接入微信支付，测试阶段就实现近万元的营收转化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从开发到收益，全链路打通。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003858\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6484375\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78cfb315&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70Psb6p8j16yiaMFzOWC0BiaR4c4uJJfDwgRdmTaYNINkALActWhibwom3RQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">案例链接：<a href=\"https://app-7qiuz0pss3cx.appmiaoda.com/#/pages/home/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://app-7qiuz0pss3cx.appmiaoda.com/#/pages/home/index</a></span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒为什么能让这些人赚钱？</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为它不只是生成代码，是从开发到商业化的完整解决方案。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术上，秒哒用的是自研模型+Agent协作的方式，多个智能体分工协作，模拟团队开发。从想法到可用的应用原型，通常3分钟就能搞定。生成的应用支持H5、Web、微信小程序，覆盖主流场景。更重要的是，一键部署，云上托管，不需要自己买服务器折腾。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">插件生态上，秒哒内置了百度的独家能力——百度AI搜索、百度地图、各种AI工具(图文生成、语音合成、文字识别等)。这些在国内做应用必备的能力，秒哒都给你准备好了。还有短信验证码、微信支付、用户登录这些本土化服务，直接集成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户要调用任何能力，只需要@一下就行，不需要看文档、写代码。我之前吐槽过传统无代码平台\"逼你学习它的程序逻辑，文档还写得很烂\"，但秒哒这种方式，学习成本几乎为零。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100003854\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=412864ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHY3jhonOG1uFh6KRibkRT70PRaXFZ1dJzu2szFY3o25Iezn5o5wjnK86E4sicy6RlOo33bxyVaZgBag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">商业化上，秒哒做得更深入。百度搜索流量扶持、模板和插件交易分成、秒哒商单平台线上接单、官方技术支持保障稳定性……不只是帮你做应用，还帮你做生意。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是为什么有人能用秒哒省140万，有人能靠秒哒赚钱。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是秒哒\"更适合中国宝宝\"的原因。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术平权，创意为王</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">VibeCoding的意义，不只是让代码生成变得更快。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">是技术平权。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">10人小团队可以做出完整产品。小学生半小时可以做出应用。普通人可以用AI赚钱。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这在以前是不可想象的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但技术不是全部。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">工具越来越强，但判断力永远是人的。AI可以帮你做，但不能帮你想。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正稀缺的，是创意、洞察和需求理解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">油气职工知道油田需要什么工具。琴行老板知道网文作者需要什么帮助。口腔教师知道家长和孩子需要什么服务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们有需求，有洞察，有想法。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒只是帮他们把想法变成了现实。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">对我来说，相比做视频、写文章而言，vibe coding去做点小产品更像是一个解压的娱乐过程，而不是工作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但对很多人来说，这可能是一个商业机会。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一批用秒哒赚钱的人，已经出现了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">下一个，可能就是你。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验链接</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">: <a href=\"https://www.miaoda.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.miaoda.cn/</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
